import React from 'react'; const SpaceList = ({spacecrafts, setListUpdated, newSpacecraft}) => { const handleDelete = id => { const requestInit = { method: 'DELETE' } fetch('http://localhost:8080/api/v1/spacecraft/' + id, requestInit) .then(res => res.json()) .then(res => console.log(res)) setListUpdated(true) } const handleUpdate = id => { const requestInit = { method: 'PUT', headers: {'Content-Type': 'application/json'}, body: JSON.stringify(newSpacecraft) } fetch('http://localhost:8080/api/v1/spacecraft/' + id, requestInit) .then(res => res.json()) .then(res => console.log(res)) setListUpdated(true) } return ( {spacecrafts.map((spacecrafts) => ( ))}
